# Shadcn Install Command
- When adding/installing shadcn components, use `bunx` (not `npx`/`npm`) to run the shadcn CLI.
- Prefer these patterns:
  - Add a component: `bunx --bun shadcn@latest add <component-name>`
- If the shadcn CLI asks additional prompts, follow the defaults that match your repo’s existing shadcn setup.
